icon|ENG}} [[Dave Hickson]]\n| align=center|'''Nov 83 \u2013 Dec 83'''\n| {{flagicon|SCO}} Alec Donald (CT)\n| align=center|'''Apr 08 \u2013 May 8'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} Jim Grattan\n|-\n| align=center|'''Jan 65 \u2013 Oct 66'''\n| {{flagicon|SCO}} George Smith\n| align=center|'''Dec 83 \u2013 Jun 84'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} [[Jim Platt]]\n| align=center|'''May 8 \u2013 Dec 11'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} [[Roy Walker (footballer)|Roy Walker]]\n|-\n| align=center|'''Dec 66 \u2013 Jan 67'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} [[Norman Clarke (footballer)|Norman Clarke]] (CT)\n| align=center|'''Jun 84 \u2013 Apr 85'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} Alan Campbell\n| align=center|'''Dec 11'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} Joe McCall (CT)\n|-\n| align=center|'''Sep 67 \u2013 Dec 67'''\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Dave Hickson]]\n| align=center|'''May 85 \u2013 Sep 87'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} Jimmy Brown\n| align=center|'''Dec 11 \u2013 Mar 16'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} [[Glenn Ferguson]]\n|}\nSource: [http://www.ballymenaunitedfc.com/history/history/managerhistory.php Ballymenaunitedfc.com]\n\n==Honours==\n===Senior honours===\n*'''[[Irish Cup]]: 6'''\n**1927\u201328*, 1939\u201340, 1957\u201358, [[1980\u201381 Irish Cup|1980\u201381]], [[1983\u201384 Irish Cup|1983\u201384]], [[1988\u201389 Irish Cup|1988\u201389]]\n*'''[[Northern Ireland Football League Cup]]: 1'''\n**[[Northern Ireland Football League Cup|2016\u201317]]\n*'''[[City Cup (Northern Ireland)|City Cup]]: 1'''\n**1971\u201372\n*'''[[Gold Cup (Northern Ireland)|Gold Cup]]: 1'''\n**1974\u201375\n*'''[[Ulster Cup]]: 3'''\n**1951\u201352**, 1960\u201361, 1980\u201381\n*'''[[IFA Premiership|Irish League First Division]]: 1'''\n**1996\u201397\n*'''[[County Antrim Shield]]: 6'''\n**1947\u201348, 1950\u201351, 1975\u201376, 1979\u201380, 2012\u201313, 2015\u201316\n\n===Intermediate honours===\n*'''[[IFA Reserve League]]: 1'''\n**2006\u201307\u2020\n*'''[[Steel & Sons Cup]]: 1'''\n**1995\u201396\u2020\n*'''Louis Moore Cup: 1'''\n**1952\u201353\u2020\n*'''[[George Wilson C