]]\n| bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|2\u20130\n| bgcolor=\"#ffffdd\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|0\u20130\n| bgcolor=\"#ddffdd\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''2\u20130'''\n|-\n| [[2019\u201320 UEFA Europa League#First qualifying round|1QR]]\n| align=\"left\"| {{flagicon|Sweden}} [[Malm\u00f6 FF|Malm\u00f6]]\n| bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|0\u20134\n| bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|0\u20137\n| bgcolor=\"#ffdddd\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''0\u201311'''\n|}\n\n==Players==\n===First team squad===\n{{updated|1 January, 2020}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Ballymena United FC|url=https://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/season=2020/clubs/club=52374/squad/|website=UEFA|accessdate=4 July 2019}}</ref>\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player|no=1|nat=Northern Ireland|pos=GK|name=Ross Glendinning}}\n{{Fs player|no=2|nat=Northern Ireland|pos=MF|name=[[Tony Kane]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=3|nat=Northern Ireland|pos=DF|name=Conor Quigley}}\n{{Fs player|no=4|nat=Northern Ireland|pos=DF|name=Jonathan Addis}}\n{{Fs player|no=5|nat=Northern Ireland|pos=DF|name=Scott Whiteside}}\n{{Fs player|no=6|nat=Northern Ireland|pos=MF|name=Ryan Mayse}}\n{{Fs player|no=7|nat=Northern Ireland|pos=MF|name=Shane McGinty}}\n{{Fs player|no=8|nat=Northern Ireland|pos=MF|name=Ryan Harpur}}\n{{Fs player|no=9|nat=Northern Ireland|pos=FW|name=Cathair Friel}}\n{{Fs player|no=11|nat=Northern Ireland|pos=DF|name=Steven McCullough}}\n{{Fs player|no=12|nat=Northern Ireland|pos=FW|name=Kenny Kane}} \n{{Fs player|no=14|nat=Northern Ireland|pos=DF|name=Andrew Burns}}\n{{fs mid}} \n{{Fs player|no=16|nat=Northern Ireland|pos=MF|name=Declan Carville}}\n{{Fs player|no=18|nat=Northern Ireland|pos=GK|name=Thomas McDermott}} \n{{Fs player|no=19|nat=Northern Ireland|pos=DF|name=Kofi Balmer}} \n{{Fs player|no=20|nat=Northern Ireland|pos=MF|name=[[Jude Winchester]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=21|nat=Northern Ireland|pos=DF|name=Jim Ervin|other=[[Captain (association football)|captain]]}}\n{{Fs player|