x McKee\n|-\n| align=center|'''Sep 37 \u2013 Nov 38'''\n| {{flagicon|SCO}} Steve Mitchell\n| align=center|'''Dec 69 \u2013 Aug 71'''\n| {{flagicon|SCO}} [[Alex McCrae]]\n| align=center|'''May 91 \u2013 Sep 93'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} [[Jim Hagan]]\n|-\n| align=center|'''Jun 46 \u2013 Sep 46'''\n| {{flagicon|SCO}} William Reid\n| align=center|'''Aug 71 \u2013 Mar 76'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} Arthur Stewart\n| align=center|'''Oct 93 \u2013 Oct 94'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} [[Tommy Jackson (footballer born 1946)|Tommy Jackson]]\n|-\n| align=center|''' Jun 47 \u2013 May 49'''\n| {{flagicon|SCO}} [[Bobby McKay]]\n| align=center|'''Mar 76 \u2013 Apr 77'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} Eddie Russell\n| align=center|'''Oct 94 \u2013 Mar 95'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} Gary Erwin\n|-\n| align=center|''' Aug 49 \u2013 May 50'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} Billy McMillan\n| align=center|'''Apr 77 \u2013 May 77'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} Alex McKee (CT)\n| align=center|'''Mar 95 \u2013 Apr 99'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} Alan Fraser\n|-\n| align=center|'''May 50 \u2013 Mar 51'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} Norman Kernaghan\n| align=center|'''May 77 \u2013 Jan 79'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} [[Billy Johnston (footballer, born 1942)|Billy Johnston]]\n| align=center|'''Apr 99 \u2013 May 99'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} Shay Hamill (CT)\n|-\n| align=center|'''Aug 53 \u2013 Jun 54'''\n| {{flagicon|SCO}} Samuel Picken\n| align=center|'''Feb 79 \u2013 Feb 82'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} Alan Campbell\n| align=center|'''May 99 \u2013 Dec 00'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} Nigel Best\n|-\n| align=center|'''Aug 54 \u2013 May 55'''\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} Walter Rickett\n| align=center|'''Feb 82 \u2013 Feb 83'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} Ivan Murray\n| align=center|'''Dec 00 \u2013 Jan 01'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} George Magill (CT)\n|-\n| align=center|'''Oct 57 \u2013 Jan 60'''\n| {{flagicon|SCO}} [[Alex McCrae]]\n| align=center|'''Feb 83 \u2013 Apr 83'''\n| {{flagicon|SCO}} Alec Donald (CT)\n| align=center|'''Jan 01 \u2013May 5'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} [[Kenny Shiels]]\n|-\n| al