hes (1980\u201381)\n*Most Clean Sheets in a Season: '''9''' in 22 matches (1980\u201381)\n\nSource: [http://www.ballymenaunitedfc.com/history/records/clubrecords.php Ballymenaunitedfc.com]\n\n===Leading goalscorers by season===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" width=\"100%\" COLOR=\"grey\"\n|-\n!width=\"5%\"|Season\n!width=\"16%\"|Name\n!width=\"4%\"|Goals\n!width=\"5%\"|Season\n!width=\"16%\"|Name\n!width=\"4%\"|Goals\n!width=\"5%\"|Season\n!width=\"16%\"|Name\n!width=\"4%\"|Goals\n|-\n| align=center|'''2010\u201311'''\n| {{flagicon|SCO}} Gary McCutcheon\n| align=center|15\n| align=center|'''1992\u201393'''\n| {{flagicon|SCO}} Neil Candlish\n| align=center|16\n| align=center|'''1974\u201375'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} Gary Erwin\n| align=center|18\n|-\n| align=center|'''2009\u201310'''\n| {{flagicon|SCO}} [[Kevin Kelbie]]\n| align=center|16\n| align=center|'''1991\u201392'''\n| {{flagicon|SCO}} Neil Candlish\n| align=center|18\n| align=center|'''1973\u201374'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} [[Paul Kirk (footballer)|Paul Kirk]]\n| align=center|30\n|-\n| align=center|'''2008\u201309'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} [[Neil Teggart]]\n| align=center|12\n| align=center|'''1990\u201391'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} Des Loughery\n| align=center|15\n| align=center|'''1972\u201373'''\n| {{flagicon|SCO}} Sammy Frickelton\n| align=center|14\n|-\n| align=center|'''2007\u201308'''\n| {{flagicon|SCO}} [[Kevin Kelbie]]\n| align=center|16\n| align=center|'''1989\u201390'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} Lindsay Curry\n| align=center|14\n| align=center|'''1971\u201372'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} Jim Martin\n| align=center|44\n|-\n| align=center|'''2006\u201307'''\n| {{flagicon|SCO}} [[Kevin Kelbie]]\n| align=center|17\n| align=center|'''1988\u201389'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} [[Paul Hardy]]\n| align=center|21\n| align=center|'''1970\u201371'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} Jim Martin\n| align=center|16\n|-\n| align=center|'''2005\u201306'''\n| {{flagicon|SCO}} [[Kevin Kelbie]]\n| align=center|16\n| align=center|'''1987\u201388'''\n| {{flagicon|NIR}} B